EPISTAR CORP (2448)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 10.78% to NT$1,510,516,000 from NT$1,692,975,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           1,510,516        1,692,975   
YOY%             -10.78%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           5,111,703        6,140,590   
YOY%             -16.76% 
=================================================================
 